{"tid":1706543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修最大防線","createTime":"2019-11-11T06:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:22:23.000Z","uid":116042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad452ee065640b038e8fdecedb66a5d8ac3eca3b","tid":1706543,"uid":116042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"其實好多時發現入唔到閘，或者花好多時間係道閘到，之後噴兩下就放棄，其實換個諗法，我地入唔到去，都唔好比佢地開到入去，應該幫佢地加固<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如用魔術鋼膠塞住道閘同電制個鎖匙燶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQq92U1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQq92U1.jpg&h=d019d4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然小弟唔係做裝修，但之前屋企有野爛左所以用，用後感真係好硬，只需五分鐘硬過印度神油，一個鐘之後要用雷震子果D錐先整得開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當佢地要開門果陣佢地自然會自己爆自己閘因為鎖匙燶太細，錐唔可以隊到入去，唔爆又無生意，爆左又要換閘，好似奇異博士咁佢地慢慢loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然可能仲有好多唔同加固方法，歡迎一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f510c65f85f6593d8e19b04de41c9a8a72350c38","tid":1706543,"uid":116042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"be731ca934479d25cff22c6fbbdf1156045928d2","tid":1706543,"uid":116042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3cb460bad1ccedcc2f88b680c21722ab76339c35","tid":1706543,"uid":116042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"335a7b66a599a8a5c21c5d9c50043691a9418ec5","tid":1706543,"uid":116042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:13:46.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2ffb06e6391354666d52a6f85f41b94ca5c48821","tid":1706543,"uid":116042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"64bd0c72a8523b0a4c00f1515cb